accessibility.text: A primeira - e, possivelmente, a mais importante - etapa no pipeline de (coleta e) análise de dados é a definição da pergunta que se quer responder.
- Would you tell me, please, which way I ought to go from here?  - That depends a good deal on where you want to get to, said the Cat.
- I don’t much care where, said Alice.
- Then it doesn’t matter which way you go, the Cat replied
